328
00:24:29,385 --> 00:24:34,812
Iowa, the greatest agricultural state
in the union...

329
00:24:35,015 --> 00:24:40,738
...gives to this convention and to the
Democratic Party its illustrious...

330
00:24:40,896 --> 00:24:44,070
...distinguished son Henry A. Wallace...

331
00:24:44,233 --> 00:24:47,533
...for this nomination of the vice
presidency of the United States.

332
00:24:49,822 --> 00:24:54,168
We want Wallace!
We want Wallace! We want Wallace!

333
00:24:55,077 --> 00:25:01,005
<i>When the first ballot ended,
