334
00:25:01,166 --> 00:25:02,839
<i>Then a second ballot got underway...</i>

335
00:25:03,002 --> 00:25:07,348
<i>...and now the deals the bosses
had made kicked into action.</i>

336
00:25:07,506 --> 00:25:11,010
<i>Jackson announced that the second
ballot would begin at once...</i>

337
00:25:11,176 --> 00:25:14,100
<i>...therefore, no new convention tickets
would be honored.</i>

338
00:25:14,263 --> 00:25:19,235
<i>Mayor Kelly's police barred thousands
more of Wallace's supporters from the hall.</i>

339
00:25:19,393 --> 00:25:23,990
<i>But those inside began chanting as before,
