382
00:28:48,644 --> 00:28:52,774
<i>Although
Churchill wanted a non-communist Poland...</i>

383
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:56,786
<i>...the truth was that Poland was simply
off the agenda...</i>

384
00:28:56,944 --> 00:29:01,666
<i>...and Churchill was more concerned
with safeguarding British power.</i>

385
00:29:01,823 --> 00:29:07,330
<i>Stalin took the paper and made a large check
