386
00:29:07,496 --> 00:29:08,668
<i>Churchill remarked:</i>

387
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:11,379
<i>Might it not be thought rather cynical...</i>

388
00:29:11,541 --> 00:29:14,636
<i>...if it seemed
we had disposed of these issues...</i>

389
00:29:14,795 --> 00:29:18,675
<i>...so fateful to millions of people
in such an offhand manner?</i>

390
00:29:18,840 --> 00:29:21,184
<i>Let us burn the paper.</i>

391
00:29:21,718 --> 00:29:26,770
<i>But Stalin urged Churchill
to hold onto the historic scrap of paper...</i>

392
00:29:26,932 --> 00:29:30,778
<i>...which Churchill called</i>
